# Cursor AI Rules for this workspace

## Language Preference
- Always use English only
- No Chinese characters anywhere in code, comments, strings, or documentation
- All variable names, function names, and text content must be in English
- When explaining concepts or writing documentation, use English only

## Code Style
- Use clear, descriptive English names for variables and functions
- Write comments in English
- Error messages and user-facing text in English
- Documentation and README files in English

## Examples
✅ Good: `def calculate_transport_cost()`
❌ Bad: `def 计算运输成本()`

✅ Good: `# Calculate the total cost`
❌ Bad: `# 计算总成本`


